  <body>
    <section name="Edit group properties">
      <span class="shortdesc">How to edit the properties of a Hippo CMS user group.</span>

   <script type="text/javascript">
    leftpx=0;
   </script>
   <div class='group'>
    <div id='screenshot'><div>
      <img src="../../../../images/screenshots/cms_M13/admins/edit_group_properties.png" alt='Edit group properties screenshot'/>
    </div></div>
   <p>About to click on the name 'inars' to edit the groups properties.
   </p>
   </div>

   <p>You will also want to set the permissions for the group, but this is not done as an edit of
    the group, but as an <a href='set_permissions_for_group.html'>edit of permissions</a>.
   </p>

   <p>You can edit the following properties of the group:
   </p>
   <ol>
    <li>
     Description.
    </li>
    <li>
     User memberships of the group. This is also possible
     as an <a href='assign_user_to_group.html'>edit of user properties</a>.
    </li>
    <li>
     Delete the group.
    </li>
   </ol>

   <p>
    When finished <a href='./save_settings.html'>save the settings</a>.
   </p>

